Paper: hep-th/9905140

Date: 1999-05-19

Title: Calculating the infrared central charges for perturbed minimal models

improving the RG perturbationAuthors: Lars Kjaergaard and Paul Mansfield

Comments: 9 pages, 3 Postscript figures, uses AMS-LaTeX

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B462 (1999) 103-108

We illustrate a method for improving Renormalisation Group improvedperturbation theory by calculating the infrared central charge of a perturbedconformal field theory. The additional input is a dispersion relation thatexploits analyticity of the energy-momentum tensor correlator.